            <section xml:id="class_square_mesh_generator_1a4bf7ccb54b42b23c4c21e6b0348cfa64">
                <title>void SquareMeshGenerator::refine_global (parallel::distributed::Triangulation&lt; 3 &gt; *in_tria, unsigned int times)</title> <emphasis>This function is intended to execute a global refinement of the mesh.</emphasis>
                
<para>This means that every cell will be refined in every direction (effectively multiplying the number of DOFs by 8). This version is the most expensive refinement possible and should be used with caution. 
                <formalpara>
                    <title/>
